<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Truncheon1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Truncheon,</orth> subst. 1) a short staff, a club, a cudgel: <cit><quote>thy leg a stick compared with this t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.10.52" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 10, 52</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) a staff of command: <bibl n="shak. mm 2.2.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 2, 61</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.3.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 3, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.2.204" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 2, 204</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 2.1.280" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 1, 280</bibl> (not in Ff).
